videos.description: Jordan Geist sends a bounce pass to Jeremiah Tilmon who jumps up for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Mizzou Tilmon throws down the hammer

videos.description: Off the rebound, Jeremiah Tilmon gets the ball and sinks turn-around jumper.
videos.headline: Tigers' Tilmon opens second half with turn-around jumper

videos.description: Missouri's Kassius Robertson drains a step-back jumper to extend their lead.
videos.headline: Robertson drains a corner triple for the Tigers

videos.description: Jontay Porter drives into the paint, and lays one in for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Mizzou's Porter drives a one in for a lay-in

videos.description: TJ Starks dribbles through the Tigers' defense for the driving layup.
videos.headline: Aggies' Starks shows off handles for layup

videos.description: Texas A&M's TJ Starks drains back-to-back triples making it a 3-point game.
videos.headline: Aggies' Starks swishes in clutch back-to-back triples
